# Development Report

## Project Title

Human Development Index (HDI) Prediction using Machine Learning

## Frontend

* HTML5
* CSS3

## Backend

* Flask (Python)

## Machine Learning

* Linear Regression
* Scikit-learn

## Dataset

* Human Development Index (HDI) Dataset

## Python Libraries

* Flask
* NumPy
* Pandas
* Matplotlib
* Seaborn
* Scikit-learn
* Pickle

## Development Workflow

1. Collected the HDI dataset.
2. Performed data preprocessing.
3. Conducted Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA).
4. Selected relevant features.
5. Trained the Linear Regression model.
6. Evaluated model performance.
7. Saved the trained model using Pickle.
8. Developed the Flask web application.
9. Connected the Machine Learning model with the Flask backend.
10. Designed the HTML user interface.
11. Tested the application.
12. Deployed the application using Render.

## Final Outcome

The project successfully predicts the Human Development Index (HDI) score using user-provided socio-economic indicators and displays the corresponding Human Development category through a user-friendly web interface.
